headline: Aetna expands initiatives to simplify experiences for health care professionals and patients
summary: Aetna®, a CVS Health® company (NYSE: CVS), today announces key milestones in support of the company's comprehensive strategy announced in June to remove friction in the healthcare system and improve the experience for healthcare professionals and their patients.
